Model shoot for gorgeous @me_soph_iya_ 

Videographer @anton_volnyanskyy 
Photo/makeup/hair @julia.yatel

Fashion video for the portfolio of the model Sofia. We shot it on a very sunny day in Cascais. The reel was meant to be a very relaxed, beautiful story. We shot in the sun and in the shade. We will show you the finished photos soon.

Sunset flow 

Shoot for gorgeous @me_soph_iya_ 
Videographer @anton_volnyanskyy 
Photo/makeup/hair by @julia.yatel 
Jewelry @houseofpearlsjewels 

A photo shoot on the beach in Portugal is always about experimentation and possibilities. We did this shoot in Cascais in October for model Sophiya. We were lucky to shoot with such beautiful light during the sunset. Sophiya, a very brave model, posed for sensual shots right next to the waves. In the end she was completely covered by the waves. Immediately afterwards we did some chic fashion shots with wet hair and wet body.
